The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions using attention mechanisms, which is a common technique in natural language processing, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve performance, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it aims to retrieve relevant information from an image to answer a question, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
